      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWO TRUTHS (4) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 24.02 beating Sekola Blue. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can make it back-to-back wins. JILLIBY PIXIE (2) is better than last start when sixth (24.88) in a Grade 7 at this track over 425m. Great chance to atone. URANA TAURUS (1) turned in a solid run last start over 525m at The Meadows finishing 5th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (30.60). Returns to favourable track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Bold showing expected. PAW IRULAN (3) was in the money last time at Horsham (23.35) in a Mix 6/7, finishing a 2.75 lengths second. Has already won out of this draw.",
